sequenceDiagram
    participant C as SimpleConsumer
    participant P as Proxy
    participant B as Broker
    participant S as 业务服务

    C->>P: Receive(max=16, invisible=30s)
    P->>B: POP/拉取消息
    B-->>P: Message + ReceiptHandle
    P-->>C: MessageView
    C->>S: 执行业务逻辑

    alt 业务成功
        S-->>C: 成功
        C->>P: Ack
        P->>B: 确认消费
    else 业务失败或进程退出
        S-->>C: 失败
        Note over C,B: 不 Ack；不可见时间结束后重新投递
    end
